headline: State Street Corporation Declares Dividends on its Common Stock and Non-Cumulative Perpetual Preferred Stock Series "G," "I," "J," and "K"
summary: BOSTON, May 14, 2025--State Street Corporation (NYSE:STT) today announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.76 per share of common stock, payable on July 11, 2025 to common shareholders of record at the close of business on July 1, 2025.
